          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="wrapper_light_bg">
    <QuoteBlock
      quote="We are absolutely thrilled with the brand identity the team at Luma developed for Midnight Coffee. From the very first mood board to the final design, they perfectly captured the 'midnight' aesthetic we were dreaming of — moody, sophisticated, and inviting. They also helped design our merch and packaging for coffee beans which has already received so many compliments from our customers."
      name="Alex Nelson"
      title="Owner"
      company="Midnight Coffee"
      personImg="/img/image_quote_alex.webp"
      logoSrc="/img/mc.svg"
    />
  </div>

